name: TIKI LAND
description:
It is Time! You are finally old enough to create your own tikimask.

--- About ---

TIKI LAND is a short and relaxing walking simulator, where you need to fulfill a row of quests. But dont worry! There are no dangers or enemies. Take your time. Talk to your neighbors and ask for their assistance.  Collect the materials you need. And most importantly of all: have fun!
